{
  "stem": "12882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That, he did in the following fashion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We would leave the house at 9:30 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We would go to one of the most beautiful museum in Dresden, only in one hall, never more, and discuss the pictures in our way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sometimes, very funny comments.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then we went on to the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The reason for it was that, at 11 o'clock, there was a high mass, and the orchestra of the opera played, and the soloists were the singers from the opera.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I am very familiar with masses by Schubert, Hayden, and Mozart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, we went on to our stores.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father would wind the clocks, and we went back home to have dinner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Sunday, the warm meal is eaten at noon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we grew up and had our own activities, my father was very, very unhappy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had to fight for every free Sunday because he felt cheated not to be able to go with us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it was a unique way of being educated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I returned to Dresden and looked at the museum and the Gemaldegalerie, and I felt totally at home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So pictures were not at the same places, but the pictures, as such, are engraved in my memory, and I know quite well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Needless to say, when I am all over the world, teaching and doing things, I do go to museums.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it's very fortunate with the career of our quartet, that I have seen very many and that we played in very many of them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well, let's go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We went to normal schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were good students.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "School didn't hamper me at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was always at the top of the class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was one subject I was at the bottom of the class, and that was physical education.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
